Product Description: Packing food, clothing, toys and accessories for your baby is convenient and made easy with the Solimo Diaper Backpack. Made using 100% polyester water resistant fabric, it is durable, long lasting and easy to clean in case of spills and accidents. This spacious backpack is made using quality materials and stitching and is tested in an NABL accredited lab against 72 parameters for quality, performance and safety. It is free from harmful chemicals like Azo dye and formaldehyde, making it safe for everyday use. For your peace of mind it comes with a 1 year warranty against manufacturing defects. The Solimo Diaper Backpack is equipped with zipper closures that are sturdy and convenient to use. Built with a quick access back opening, it leads directly to the interior of the bag and can be used with one hand. This backpack features an insulated pocket that can store 3 feeding bottles with ease. A side tissue pocket is zipperless and easy to reach and pull out. This backpack also has a back mobile pocket that is discrete to help prevent theft. With shoulder and tote carrying straps, you can decide which is more comfortable for you. From diapers, towels, tissues, feeding bottles and toys, this diaper backpack is ideal for park trips, outings and everyday activities.
